- To the East Tunnel!

345
00:22:57.810 --> 00:22:58.711
Shit! Go. go!

346
00:23:04.817 --> 00:23:06.652
It's collapsed!

347
00:23:06.653 --> 00:23:08.854
We don't have
any other choice!

348
00:23:18.164 --> 00:23:19.798
